__cs__ Tracy was doing what so many of us do when we feel like we &apos;ve put in a good day in the job search .
__cs__ She was looking for a finance or accounting role , and she had just spent the last nine months very diligently researching companies online and applying for jobs with no results .
__cs__ I met Tracy in June of 2011 , when the Today Show asked me if I could work with her to see if I could help her turn things around .
